Agenda

	* What is a text file ?
	* Create a text file in java ?
	* Delete a text file in java ?
	* Read text from a text file in java ?
	* Write text into a text file in java ?
	* Perform the read and write operations in multiple ways ?


	Note :- Different ways of reading the data from text files
		* FileInputStream
		* Scanner
		* FileReader
		* BufferedReader

	note: - If we are using anyone of this we must close after completing of our task.
			For security purpose, if we not close this chance of memory leaks.


	Note:- Different ways of writing the data into text files
	        * FileOutputStream
	        * FileWriter
	        * BufferedWriter

	        Scanner cannot write it can only read.

	Note:- We don't have any method to update
	       To do that we First Reader the file and Do change or adding text
	       and update the file using writer